{"tid":2357471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）新冠肺炎︰男患者聲稱跟護士醫院內性交　或囚10年","createTime":"2021-01-07T12:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T12:37:46.000Z","uid":333488,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74af82aa81789965f8379833b2fcae753f16c988","tid":2357471,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"澳洲傳媒周三（30日）報道，印尼首都雅加達一名新冠肺炎確診男患者日前在社交網聲稱，與一名脫去個人防護裝備的女護士在隔離中心的洗手間內性交。院方向2人問話，2人直認不諱。涉事女護士已遭停職。<br />\n涉事男子上周五（25日）在Twitter上載貼文炫耀，並附上圖片，可見防護裝備被丟下，散落一地。他還貼出與護士的對話，惹來網民口誅筆伐。院方事後再為2人檢測，男子仍然未痊愈，女護士則未有確診。2人或會遭檢控妨礙風化罪，最高可囚10年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNf3wiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNf3wiK.jpg&h=2da617e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以為日本AV添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9b829ff365734995b45014d81f883b0a8ce21f","tid":2357471,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"女護士冇確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4179cd24ba61b9481edbac9dab7784fbb76bacbb","tid":2357471,"uid":388592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"係咪陳雲Fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n弱感冒啫，唔怕！"},{"pid":"938459deaee6d648b6136d9bd37da78d8fcfcd2e","tid":2357471,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"原來有武肺有閪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9195a26e211d8ce0ae908d2ac0f2877291d09a","tid":2357471,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c9b829ff365734995b45014d81f883b0a8ce21f","tid":2357471,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"女護士冇確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited